      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of June 29 article about Supreme Court decision regarding Boy Scouts; article misstated position of United Methodist Church; although church opposes discrimination based on sexual orientation, it does not encourage congregations to sever ties with Boy Scouts (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on Thursday about groups that disagreed with the Supreme Court ruling allowing the Boy Scouts of America to exclude gays misstated the position of the United Methodist Church. Although the church opposes discrimination based on sexual orientation, it did not encourage congregations to sever ties with the Boy Scouts.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
